1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,420
I can't believe she's gone.

2
00:00:01,860 --> 00:00:04,280
She'd be alive today if we hadn't dragged
her into this.

3
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:06,720
Teresa died the way she lived,
doing what she believed in.

4
00:00:06,840 --> 00:00:09,020
In any case, you could hardly have stopped
her.

5
00:00:09,180 --> 00:00:09,800
No one could.

6
00:00:09,900 --> 00:00:11,420
She gave her life for mine.

7
00:00:11,640 --> 00:00:12,920
How can I live with that?

8
00:00:13,060 --> 00:00:14,060
The same way I will.

9
00:00:14,720 --> 00:00:15,720
By surviving.

10
00:00:16,020 --> 00:00:17,160
By not giving up.

11
00:00:17,400 --> 00:00:19,040
By fighting for what you believe in.

12
00:00:19,540 --> 00:00:20,760
It's not over yet.

13
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:31,580
You could have ended it here.

14
00:00:31,860 --> 00:00:36,821
A secretary of state when the administration
falls, you would have the power.

15
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:38,040
No.

16
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:40,540
I have other plans for Gabriel Logan.

17
00:00:40,980 --> 00:00:44,260
Hearings have been scheduled and I need
someone to blame.

